query:
INSERT INTO static.route_stop (route_id, source, stop_id, stop_sequence, data)
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::TEXT[],
                $2::source_enum[],
                $3::TEXT[],
                $4::SMALLINT[],
                $5::JSONB[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (route_id, source, stop_id) DO UPDATE SET
                stop_sequence = EXCLUDED.stop_sequence,
                data = EXCLUDED.data
